text: Hedong Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Qingyuan District, Ji'an, Jiangxi province, China. , it has 8 residential communities and 11 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Jiangxi == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Jiangxi Category:Ji'an
